{"tid":129663,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"算唔算抑鬱？","createTime":"2017-02-21T18:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T08:24:26.000Z","uid":72252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66d7846f40b6ad30e6df1ad138b8cddeca0df7c2","tid":129663,"uid":72252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T18:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 晚晚都喊算唔算抑鬱？已經成個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜都冇心機做、胃口變差又失眠、好難集中精神、個人好易攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係極唔想死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：讀緊書<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點樣搵醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46aa61431d8c06c478b9d4c11461fa1ef7b74efd","tid":129663,"uid":72252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T18:51:15.000Z","msg":"毒撚冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1262647aeb2027717b71c22f3b0ed6c7d75e9b","tid":129663,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T20:13:46.000Z","msg":"如果唔開心係佔你9成時間<br />\n<br />\n係<br />\n但未有自殺傾向<br />\n我以前都係<br />\n唔怕 只會開細劑量藥<br />\n血清應該夠你用<br />\n<br />\nbtw 我最後係做運動+ 有拖拍就無食lu"},{"pid":"aa2d8a438641fd34ff07b51842e08ac251fd54e3","tid":129663,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T20:15:06.000Z","msg":"先找社工或心理輔導"},{"pid":"452ca1d43c3132730f8e6cb0aa94e6f9665041ab","tid":129663,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T20:16:25.000Z","msg":"最快最抵方法<br />\n私家醫生<br />\n叫佢幫你轉介公立<br />\n好快有<br />\n但小心醫院出入<br />\n好撚多烏糟野見你唔開心跟你<br />\n到時仲仆街<br />\n搵屋企人陪你去睇 正面啲 抬起頭 盡量精神啲去見醫生<br />\n你係好驚既話就戴定黑曜石去<br />\n<br />\n過來人"},{"pid":"32c2e48f981d5a8080e94436f463e104c4228d1d","tid":129663,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T20:19:17.000Z","msg":"講下發生咗乜事"},{"pid":"6ba951b062a798313e0206cec0fa25d9feb996a3","tid":129663,"uid":27793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T20:21:23.000Z","msg":"我覺得心理學家... 無社工咁親切<br />\n而社工無朋友咁親切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日無野同社工/心理學家講<br />\n<br />\n我係逼自己講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我需要既只係佢地血清素<br />\n<br />\n由細到大我都係咁<br />\n好難開心<br />\n醫生話某啲人係天生缺乏唔知咩製造快樂情緒既一樣物質<br />\n而血清素可以幫你製造<br />\n<br />\nbtw醫生推介跑步<br />\n3年後既今日我先培養左呢個好習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n運動都可以幫你製快樂因子<br />\n同埋食下香蕉<br />\n<br />\n最好有朋友/ 女友/ 男友<br />\n親人扶持其實最重要"},{"pid":"a9de3d7dd42aeebb4418444c72e22855709a8922","tid":129663,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T20:25:39.000Z","msg":"之前睇過醫生<br />\n話長期先算抑鬱症<br />\n不過都可以睇下精神科 <br />\n醫生會同你傾下計 會開d輕劑殘餘既藥<br />\n會好返架唔使擔心"},{"pid":"dac47d5a2ebc9cb836d03a9759c8546fc1a17844","tid":129663,"uid":72531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T20:27:04.000Z","msg":"建議巴打睇睇醫生先 始終醫生先係專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad52c73519d5d71df5dc28a446de62ce98788e06","tid":129663,"uid":19134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T20:45:56.000Z","msg":"有抑鬱症狀 但極唔想死即係冇自殺念頭 未去到最嚴重 建議你趁仲未嚴重 去睇下醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 心理學jj"},{"pid":"430ddc35a2310e3142bec6fc0e0162de1f9d40ee","tid":129663,"uid":72252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T12:10:27.000Z","msg":"多謝樓上幾位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfc52ce73d33b87d2eb311fbfddd5eef4f552dc","tid":129663,"uid":86541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T13:26:55.000Z","msg":"點解會晚晚喊<br />\n係咪有心事<br />\n不過跑步對情緒差係幾好"},{"pid":"c1ff256f9a3a8a0b520727565b2a19f5996f8638","tid":129663,"uid":72252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T16:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解會晚晚喊<br />\n係咪有心事<br />\n不過跑步對情緒差係幾好</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能幾樣唔開心嘅嘢加埋就晚晚喊<br />\n我真係好想跑步同返學<br />\n有好幾日都係換好哂衫 但冇勇氣行出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23d1d31d25768a41e650cb0f59d4e8189fb95fb","tid":129663,"uid":86541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T16:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解會晚晚喊<br />\n係咪有心事<br />\n不過跑步對情緒差係幾好</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能幾樣唔開心嘅嘢加埋就晚晚喊<br />\n我真係好想跑步同返學<br />\n有好幾日都係換好哂衫 但冇勇氣行出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n總要行出第一步 唔係會後悔"},{"pid":"8b23b18d5a04d2a354653ed78232f02680a5bddd","tid":129663,"uid":72252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T16:44:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解會晚晚喊<br />\n係咪有心事<br />\n不過跑步對情緒差係幾好</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能幾樣唔開心嘅嘢加埋就晚晚喊<br />\n我真係好想跑步同返學<br />\n有好幾日都係換好哂衫 但冇勇氣行出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n總要行出第一步 唔係會後悔</blockq